Relative R:IR ratios were calculated according to the spectral analysis data in Fig. 1 and Table 1. Under the assay conditions employed, while light intensity is constant, temperature varies. When seedlings are exposed to a spectral radiation of wavelength λ and photon flux Nλ, the relative R:IR ratio is given as follows:r(T1,T2)=NRNIR(T2)NRNIR(T1)=NIR(T1)NIR(T2)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
